{"ID":270225, "Text":"<div class=\"page\"><div class=\"pageNum\"><a name=\"225\"><\/a><div class=\"prev\"><a href=\"stpjs224.html\">Prev<\/a><\/div><div class=\"next\"><a href=\"stpjs226.html\">Next<\/a><\/div>\n\t\t\t    STPJS 225<\/div>\n  <p class=\"cont\">he further remarked, there could be no evil in it, if God gave His sanction by healing; that there\n  could be no more sin in any female laying hands on and praying for the sick, than in wetting the face\n  with water; it is no sin for anybody to administer that has faith,<span class=\"footRef\">1<\/span> or if the sick have faith to be healed<span class=\"footRef\">2<\/span>\n  by their administration.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">He reproved those that were disposed to find fault<span class=\"footRef\">3<\/span> with the management of the concerns of the\n  Church, saying God had called him to lead the Church, and he would lead it right; those that\n  undertake to interfere will be ashamed when their own folly is made manifest;<span class=\"footRef\">4<\/span> that he calculates to\n  organize the Church in its proper order as soon as the Temple is completed.<\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">Aspiring Men<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">President Smith continued by speaking of the difficulties he had to surmount ever since the\n  commencement of the work, in consequence of aspiring men.<span class=\"footRef\">5<\/span> &ldquo;Great big Elders,&rdquo; as he called them,\n  who caused him much trouble; to whom he had taught the things of the kingdom in private councils,\n  they would then go forth into the world and proclaim the things he had taught them, as their own\n  revelations; said the same aspiring disposition will be in this Society, and must be guarded against;\n  that every person should stand, and act in the place appointed,<span class=\"footRef\">6<\/span> and thus sanctify the Society and get\n  it pure. He said he had been trampled under foot<span class=\"footRef\">7<\/span> by aspiring Elders, for all were infected with that\n  spirit; for instance, John E. Page and others had been aspiring;<span class=\"footRef\">8<\/span> they could not be exalted, but must\n  run away as though the care and authority of the Church were vested with them. He said he had a\n  subtle devil<span class=\"footRef\">9<\/span> to deal with, and could only curb him by being humble.<\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">The Prophet&rsquo;s Intimation of His Death<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">As he had this opportunity, he was going to instruct the ladies of this Society, and point out the\n  way<span class=\"footRef\">10<\/span> for them to conduct themselves,<span class=\"footRef\">11<\/span> that they might act according to the will of God;<span class=\"footRef\">12<\/span> that he\n  did not know that he should have many opportunities of teaching them, as they were going to be left\n  to themselves;<span class=\"footRef\">13<\/span> they would not long have him to instruct them; that the Church would not have his\n  instructions long, and the world would not be troubled with him a great while, and would not have\n  his teachings [in person].<\/p>\n  <div class=\"footnotes\">\n    <div class=\"footnote\">1. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110383\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110383)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110383)\">James 5:14-15<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">2. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109099\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109099)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109099)\">Acts 14:9<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113763\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113763)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113763)\">D&amp;C 42:48<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113916\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113916)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113916)\">D&amp;C 46:19<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">3. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107539\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107539)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107539)\">Dan. 6:4<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108594\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108594)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108594)\">Luke 23:4<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109334\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109334)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109334)\">Rom. 9:19<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110230\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110230)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110230)\">Heb. 8:8<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112504\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112504)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112504)\">Hel. 13:28<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114925\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114925)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114925)\">D&amp;C 88:124<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">4. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110066\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110066)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110066)\">2 Tim. 3:9<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114163\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114163)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114163)\">D&amp;C 63:15<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116577\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116577)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116577)\">D&amp;C 136:19<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">5. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115811\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115811)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115811)\">D&amp;C 121:35<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">6. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115524\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115524)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115524)\">D&amp;C 107:99<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">7. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107876\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107876)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107876)\">Matt. 7:6<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">8. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115812\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115812)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115812)\">D&amp;C 121:35<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116011\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116011)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116011)\">D&amp;C 124:84<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">9. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"105972\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 105972)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(105972)\">Gen. 3:1<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111897\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111897)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111897)\">Alma 12:4<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">10. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112226\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112226)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112226)\">Alma 37:40<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">11. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112256\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112256)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112256)\">Alma 39:11<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113325\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113325)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113325)\">D&amp;C 19:41<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116529\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116529)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116529)\">D&amp;C 134:10<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">12. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109310\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109310)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109310)\">Rom. 8:27<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110468\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110468)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110468)\">1 Pet. 4:19<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112547\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112547)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112547)\">3 Ne. 5:14<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113929\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113929)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113929)\">D&amp;C 46:30<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">13. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108782\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108782)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108782)\">John 13:33<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>"}